Fortress of Fear-Formerly Dragon Cavern25 levels of action and puzzles.Requires the full version of Wolfenstein 3D.Original Readme included. Read for details.How to InstallPut the scenarios you want to play into the "Levels" folder. Open Wolfenstein 3D. You'll see the name of the scenario. Select it and click OK.Josh Millscopperfield@worldnet.att.nethttp://www.geocities.com/TelevisionCity/1568/wolf.html